Puppet module: munin

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages munin software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include munin              # Install and run munin with standard configurations.
include munin::disable     # Disable munin service.
include munin::disableboot # Disable munin service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include munin::absent      # Remove munin package.

DEPENDENCIES:
